# 🎯 Main Objective: Create a Context Transfer Document

- [ ] 1. Initialize transfer document
  - [ ] 1.1. Create new markdown file
    ```markdown
    # Context Transfer Document - [Date]
    ```
  - [ ] 1.2. Add document metadata
    ```markdown
    - From: [Current Agent]
    - To: [Target Agent]
    - Task: [Task Name]
    ```

- [ ] 2. Document key context
  - [ ] 2.1. Summarize important decisions
    ```markdown
    ## 📝 Key Decisions
    - Selected X technology because...
    - Agreed on Y approach due to...
    ```
  - [ ] 2.2. List modified files
    ```markdown
    ## 📁 Modified Files
    1. path/to/file1.ext - [Brief change description]
    2. path/to/file2.ext - [Brief change description]
    ```
  - [ ] 2.3. Document current progress
    ```markdown
    ## 📊 Progress
    - Feature X: 80% complete
    - Tests: 60% complete
    ```

- [ ] 3. Define next actions
  - [ ] 3.1. List pending tasks
    ```markdown
    ## ⏭️ Next Steps
    1. Implement [specific feature]
    2. Complete [specific task]
    ```
  - [ ] 3.2. Document blockers
    ```markdown
    ## 🚧 Blockers
    - Waiting for [specific resource]
    - Need decision on [specific item]
    ```

- [ ] 4. Verify and transfer
  - [ ] 4.1. Review document completeness
  - [ ] 4.2. Get user confirmation
  - [ ] 4.3. Share document with target agent
